    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 \u2728 **Exceptional Find \u2014 Mint Condition Gem!** We are absolutely thrilled to present this stunning vehicle, and we mean it when we say it's in mint condition! Every inch of this car reflects meticulous care \u2014 the exterior gleams with flawless paint, the interior is spotless and fresh, and everything runs and functions exactly as it should. This is the kind of car that turns heads in a parking lot and makes every drive a pleasure. Whether you're a discerning buyer looking for a worry-free ownership experience or simply want the best, this is your car. No surprises, no hidden issues \u2014 just a truly outstanding vehicle ready to impress from day one. Don't miss your chance to own something this special! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 buyers should approach this as a project car or a bare-bones transportation option rather than a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows significant wear, including rust, dents, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery, cracked trim, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to operate dependably \u2014 expect to invest additional money beyond the purchase price to bring it up to a roadworthy standard. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a parts vehicle, or a person with a very tight budget who understands and accepts the risks involved. There are no warranties implied or offered, and the car is sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "terse_6_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "terse_6",
      "description": "A mint-condition car in flawless shape, showing no wear and performing like new \u2014 a rare find for buyers who want the best.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $46,500, a price that honestly reflects its mint condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that exceptional standard means. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint is deep, rich, and uniform with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks. Panel gaps are tight and consistent throughout, and all trim pieces, chrome accents, and glass surfaces are pristine. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, the carpets are spotless, and every control, button, and display functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, corrosion, or signs of neglect. Mechanically, this car performs with full confidence: the engine starts immediately, idles smoothly, and delivers strong, responsive power across all driving conditions. The transmission shifts crisply, the brakes are firm and effective, and the suspension feels tight with no unusual noises or vibrations. All safety systems, electronics, and convenience features are fully operational. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and truly lives up to the mint designation.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Budget-Friendly & Ready for a New Chapter \u2014 A Practical Option for the Right Buyer! This used car is in poor condition, and we want to be upfront about that. It has visible wear both inside and out, and will likely need some mechanical attention to get it running at its best. That said, it's priced to reflect exactly what it is \u2014 a real opportunity for a handy buyer, a project enthusiast, or someone who needs basic transportation on a tight budget. What you see is what you get, and at this price, there's real value here for the right person! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly mint condition \u2014 a designation we apply only when a car genuinely earns it. The exterior is immaculate, presenting a deep, lustrous finish with absolutely no scratches, dents, chips, or blemishes of any kind. The interior is equally pristine: every surface, seat, and panel looks and feels as though it has barely been touched, with no wear, staining, or fading to speak of. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, running with smooth, responsive power and no unusual noises or hesitation. All mechanical and electrical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, lighting, climate control, infotainment \u2014 are fully operational and performing exactly as intended. The tires retain excellent tread depth and are evenly worn, and all fluids are fresh and at proper levels. Service records are available and reflect consistent, attentive care throughout the vehicle's life. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a car that truly requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic attention, no deferred maintenance. A buyer can drive this vehicle home with complete confidence.",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
